item.title: CVE-2023-3299|2023-07-19T23:35:12.990Z -- hashicorp -- nomad%20enterprise
item.description: HashiCorp Nomad Enterprise 1.2.11 up to 1.5.6, and 1.4.10 ACL policies using a block without a label generates unexpected results. Fixed in 1.6.0, 1.5.7, and 1.4.11.
